<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Frosty" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Frosty,</orth> causing congelation, very cold: <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.3.53" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 3, 53</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 1.3.295" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 3, 295</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 3.1.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. III, 1, 5</bibl>. Used of hair, == grey, hoary: <cit><quote>the f. head,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 5.1.167" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B V, 1, 167</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>my f. signs and chaps of age,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 5.3.77" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. V, 3, 77</bibl></cit>. Metaphorically, == cold: <bibl n="shak. ven 36" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 4.1.128" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A IV, 1, 128</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.5.22" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 5, 22</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.5.22" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 5, 22</bibl>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>